## Modifications

The installer copies upstream skill files verbatim — no renames, no
content modifications. Installed copies live outside this repository
(`~/.claude/skills/`) and are refreshed by re-running the installer.

The cross-reference edits made to *this* repository's existing files
(under `references/` and `agents/`) cite these skills by path; they do
not modify the upstream sources.
